data.title: 以 3 到 5 分钟描写以下主题
data.content: What is the most important change you want to make in your life in the next year? Explain your reasonining.
data.answer: I am planning to live a more relaxed life in the next year. The reason for this is that I am currently doing a double degree bachelor, and both of the degrees are STEM courses. So, both of those are very intense. I have been over-exhausted for a long time and I miss my life when I have the time and essence to do something I like, for example making handicrafts. I am planning to love myself more. (78 words)
